===Etymology===
Named by its discoverer {{w|Paul Emile Lecoq de Boisbaudran|Lecoq}}, after {{etyl|la}} {{term|Gallia||Gaul|lang=la}}. It was claimed that Lecoq had named the element after himself, since {{term|gallus|lang=la}} is the Latin translation of the French ''le {{term|coq|lang=fr}}'', but Lecoq denied this in an article of 1877.

